def reorderList(head):
    if not head:
        return
    slow, fast = head, head
    while fast and fast.next:
        slow = slow.next
        fast = fast.next.next

    prev, curr = None, slow.next
    slow.next = None
    while curr:
        tmp = curr.next
        curr.next = prev
        prev = curr
        curr = tmp

    first, second = head, prev
    while second:
        tmp1, tmp2 = first.next, second.next
        first.next = second
        second.next = tmp1
        first, second = tmp1, tmp2
